overview: Kasabian bring special guests and huge hits to close day one of Reading 2017.  Setlist: Ill Ray (The King), Bumblebeee, Eez-Eh (Daft Punk's "Around The World" outro), Underdog, Shoot the Runner, You're in Love With a Psycho, I.D., Club Foot, Re-Wired, Treat, Empire, Bless This Acid House, Stevie, All Apologies(Nirvana cover), L.S.F. (Lost Souls Forever)  Encore: Comeback Kid, Vlad the Impaler, Fire
title: Kasabian: Live at Reading Festival
